dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"睇洗介賴啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"係冼 唔係洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"喺邊到架請問？"},{"pid":"b8066ac25e69ded1c617285d5d91c28be8a299c7","tid":1117450,"uid":50950,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:42:56.000Z","msg":"樓主你呢隻藥膏係稀釋左，low dose來的。稀釋嘅原因可能醫生認為你唔需要咁強度嘅類固醇，小朋友都會用到呢隻濃度，至於點搽個個醫生pratctice都會有唔同，一般類固醇建議7至14日，有d人可能叫佢搽幾日就停，視乎咩位置，有幾嚴重<br />\n<br />\n利申，喺診所工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04a471d745d15421453a5a03b14c59d8d2ce44c","tid":1117450,"uid":184233,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"feaaab9c6259018e46fae790312f905ed0b1c469","tid":1117450,"uid":216472,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f838ce95a585406c85a4a07dd588c33ad46fc29","tid":1117450,"uid":184233,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"787976f1758c31d9685c4203c57d48a540758db1","tid":1117450,"uid":236691,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T18:27:23.000Z","msg":"睇洗介賴啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-21T19:23:44.000Z","msg":"係冼 唔係洗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:31:49.000Z","msg":"喺邊到架請問？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:48:08.000Z","msg":"最出名嘅皮膚科黑市醫生 <br />\n但真係醫得好好嘅<br />\n 我濕疹十幾年<br />\n睇咗佢之後半年好返  係斷尾個種好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43b71d4061b65ff40463c04835a9220b8ad07be","tid":1117450,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47277ed9a95f804786cf65a7e5e27f28d7289f5","tid":1117450,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9073e7ec0472e044f430e67c79863c1354cb5841","tid":1117450,"uid":77646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"咁你仲有咩好問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲補茶啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"就係想問下有冇人係適當用類固醇下可以好好咁控制濕疹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"用類固醇好好控制濕疹都做到嘅&hellip;<br />\n由本身急性濕疹成手傷口不停滲膿<br />\n到過咗兩年宜家冇大爆發<br />\n只有局部地方兩三個月有少少濕疹發起，一發起就搽類固醇算就撳著，唔算控制到？"},{"pid":"c1c7723f28e97b11fc6b78175cc5215c3eee4f59","tid":1117450,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"仲有想提一提樓主，如果要用類固醇，千祈唔好搽眼皮位，呢個位係吸收得最快嘅地方，容易入血，入咗血會容易加重全身病情"},{"pid":"d52b48b7971cb553650dfe163e4fff7377951dda","tid":1117450,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1c7723f28e97b11fc6b78175cc5215c3eee4f59","tid":1117450,"uid":84524,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T14:44:25.000Z","msg":"仲有想提一提樓主，如果要用類固醇，千祈唔好搽眼皮位，呢個位係吸收得最快嘅地方，容易入血，入咗血會容易加重全身病情"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:02:53.000Z","msg":"係, 另外搽眼皮會有青光眼"},{"pid":"359969bbf6ce8961348ccff0e8e2ed3a46366df9","tid":1117450,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43b71d4061b65ff40463c04835a9220b8ad07be","tid":1117450,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e47277ed9a95f804786cf65a7e5e27f28d7289f5","tid":1117450,"uid":111474,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9073e7ec0472e044f430e67c79863c1354cb5841","tid":1117450,"uid":77646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:01:45.000Z","msg":"咁你仲有咩好問？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲補茶啦！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-04-22T07:18:19.000Z","msg":"就係想問下有冇人係適當用類固醇下可以好好咁控制濕疹"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-24T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"用類固醇好好控制濕疹都做到嘅&hellip;<br />\n由本身急性濕疹成手傷口不停滲膿<br />\n到過咗兩年宜家冇大爆發<br />\n只有局部地方兩三個月有少少濕疹發起，一發起就搽類固醇算就撳著，唔算控制到？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T19:04:03.000Z","